<template>
  <v-container>
    <v-row>
      <v-col cols="6">
        <v-btn outlined color="#325d79" @click="showDialogCreateUser = true">Crear Usuario</v-btn>
      </v-col>
      <v-col cols="6">
        <v-text-field
          outlined
          color="#325d79"
          v-model="search"
          label="Buscar Usuario"
          dense
          prepend-inner-icon="fa-search"
        ></v-text-field>
      </v-col>
      <v-col cols="12">
        <v-data-table :headers="headers" :items="users" :search="search" class="elevation-5">
          <template v-slot:top>
            <v-toolbar flat color="#325d79" dark>
              <v-toolbar-title>Usuarios Registrados</v-toolbar-title>
              <v-divider class="mx-4" inset vertical></v-divider>
              <v-spacer></v-spacer>
            </v-toolbar>
          </template>
          <template v-slot:item.actions="{}">
            <v-icon class="mr-4" @click="showDialogEditUser = true">fa-edit</v-icon>
            <v-icon @click="showDialogDelete = true">fa-trash-alt</v-icon>
          </template>
        </v-data-table>
      </v-col>
    </v-row>

    <DialogCreate
      title="Crear Usuario"
      variable="usuario"
      :roles="roles"
      :piscicolas="piscicolas"
      v-model="showDialogCreateUser"
    />
    <DialogCreate
      title="Editar Usuario"
      variable="usuario"
      :roles="roles"
      :piscicolas="piscicolas"
      v-model="showDialogEditUser"
    />

    <DialogDelete title="usuario" v-model="showDialogDelete" />
  </v-container>
</template>

<script>
import DialogDelete from '@/components/DialogDelete.vue'
import DialogCreate from '@/components/DialogCreate.vue'
export default {
  components: {
    DialogDelete,
    DialogCreate
  },
  data() {
    return {
      search: '',
      showDialogCreateUser: false,
      showDialogDelete: false,
      showDialogEditUser: false,
      piscicolas: [
        {
          text: 'Pisicola1',
          value: 0
        },
        {
          text: 'Pisciola2',
          value: 1
        }
      ],
      roles: [
        {
          text: 'Administrador',
          value: 0
        },
        {
          text: 'Piscicultor',
          value: 1
        },
        {
          text: 'Trabajador',
          value: 2
        }
      ],
      headers: [
        {
          text: 'Usuario',
          value: 'nombre_usuario'
        },
        {
          text: 'Telefono',
          sortable: false,
          value: 'telefono'
        },
        {
          text: 'Rol',
          value: 'rol'
        },
        {
          text: 'Correo',
          value: 'correo'
        },
        {
          text: 'Acción',
          sortable: false,
          value: 'actions'
        }
      ],
      users: [
        {
          nombre_usuario: 'Viviana',
          telefono: 3213213123,
          rol: 'Admin',
          correo: 'viviana@ejemplo.com'
        },
        {
          nombre_usuario: 'Iván',
          telefono: 3213725289,
          rol: 'Admin',
          correo: 'ivan@ejemplo.com'
        }
      ]
    }
  }
}
</script>

<style lang="scss" scoped></style>
